{title: Italic Markup}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[Am]Whispered words in <i>italic style</i>
[Em]Gentle like a [Am]breeze
[Dm]Leaning letters <i>soft and mild</i>
[Am]Rustling through the [Em]trees
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[F]<i>Every word in italics here</i>
[C]<i>Slanted, flowing, crystal clear</i>
[G]Normal text is [Am]back again
{end_of_chorus}
